{"tid":150992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇\"新聞噏乜9\" 呢個page?","createTime":"2017-03-10T13:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T16:10:29.000Z","uid":66260,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42fb23cb35eafade62b96113be883109f526aa57","tid":150992,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T13:23:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/upmud9.nu/?hc_ref=NEWSFEED \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fupmud9.nu%2F%3Fhc_ref%3DNEWSFEED%20&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=1a8751a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/upmud9.nu/?hc_ref=NEWSFEED </a><br />\n<br />\n原本呢個page幾好笑 <br />\n但近排愈黎愈覺得佢走火入魔, 吹毛求疵 <br />\n有時明顯只係排版錯左甚至打漏左個標點就放大黎笑 <br />\n<br />\n最離譜既一D傷亡意外死人既新聞 <br />\n只係因為錯少少野都會拎黎笑, 仲要係好撚mean果隻 <br />\n有冇諗過家屬睇到會點? 簡直係傷口上灑鹽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例子: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/upmud9.nu/photos/a.532424150168315.1073741828.532415746835822/1098145230262868/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fupmud9.nu%2Fphotos%2Fa.532424150168315.1073741828.532415746835822%2F1098145230262868%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=73b34e68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/upmud9.nu/photos/a.532424150168315.1073741828.532415746835822/1098145230262868/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n正正常常講下毒果有咩語病咪得 <br />\n9up一大堆野on9當有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01bd1f158362f8f11bdef5c9ab85d62fdaedd01","tid":150992,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:07:06.000Z","msg":"篇嘢的確1999喎"},{"pid":"7dcab02369ac1fa80697cad42c4d0e60c7e57c38","tid":150992,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:07:30.000Z","msg":"btw樓豬想宣傳呀?"},{"pid":"59cce8a1001972a630baece278d9d344bb15321d","tid":150992,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"新聞媒體有責任確保佢邊文唔會出錯<br />\n何況今次篇文錯到離晒大浦"},{"pid":"611d397b2c096f8c16fbf4cd60ad76810d2c6562","tid":150992,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw樓豬想宣傳呀?</blockquote><br />\n邊個得閒宣傳呢個page?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家我明顯係插呢個page吹毛求庛"},{"pid":"9fd8f6aa94a1c8e08ac468b676cd0dc7c232a448","tid":150992,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:22:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>篇嘢的確1999喎</blockquote><br />\n6. 正常家庭對話：「<span style=\"color: red;\">老公，你食咗嗰女未啊</span>？」 #<span style=\"color: red;\">為食女立志要生女</span><br />\n7. 收到女兒昏迷床上，<span style=\"color: red;\">邊個速遞佢個女俾喺街嘅阿媽</span>？<br />\n<br />\n我同意佢1999, 但對一單不幸有人逝世既新聞黎講<br />\n以上紅字絕對係on9當有趣"},{"pid":"21843bb90dda58680f45679a2b3667295799b367","tid":150992,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>篇嘢的確1999喎</blockquote><br />\n6. 正常家庭對話：「<span style=\"color: red;\">老公，你食咗嗰女未啊</span>？」 #<span style=\"color: red;\">為食女立志要生女</span><br />\n7. 收到女兒昏迷床上，<span style=\"color: red;\">邊個速遞佢個女俾喺街嘅阿媽</span>？<br />\n<br />\n我同意佢1999, 但對一單不幸有人逝世既新聞黎講<br />\n以上紅字絕對係on9當有趣</blockquote><br />\n咁d報紙又有幾認真呢？咁都寫得出。<br />\n<br />\n或者佢地係呢d事要嚴肅d唔好講笑咁，就咁指出錯誤。"},{"pid":"00104d993a2b0b1ce10426de4de8112183cecf09","tid":150992,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:25:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新聞媒體有責任確保佢邊文唔會出錯<br />\n何況今次篇文錯到離晒大浦</blockquote><br />\n關於出街新聞既錯誤我覺得抵插<br />\n但係連一D即時突發既新聞, 錯左少少排版甚至標點都要吹毛求庛我絕對覺得係為鬧而鬧"},{"pid":"d3becfbf6fdb55597b726cb149f1a4d90fc1ecc1","tid":150992,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:25:36.000Z","msg":"同埋有d好離譜<br />\n<br />\n法國慶⼀⼁⼀"},{"pid":"55d38f4f083481b33af8b0fe9e02f1605a579e14","tid":150992,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:26:22.000Z","msg":"冇問題喎<br />\n點睇都係毒果走火入魔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b84525b29e9ab157b8b38ad95071d49bb1a1ad9","tid":150992,"uid":1788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋有d好離譜<br />\n<br />\n法國慶⼀⼁⼀</blockquote><br />\n星島連 法國慶恐襲 都寫得出係頭版"},{"pid":"3a2ba2c121ee42cbfef4397e8b2dc2bb8b19275c","tid":150992,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:30:05.000Z","msg":"有時幾高質 係挑到垃圾記者機<br />\n有時就同垃圾記者一樣垃圾,<br />\n好似仲係親熱血公民"},{"pid":"786daad12ceb4c263d79b657329ae79284c26912","tid":150992,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時幾高質 係挑到垃圾記者機<br />\n有時就同垃圾記者一樣垃圾,<br />\n好似仲係親熱血公民</blockquote><br />\n早排先俾熱狗鬧係本民青page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a28d3f9539493139e88b07f8d03b9ccf877342d","tid":150992,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:30:57.000Z","msg":"一年幾之前呢個page搞左個年度最9大獎<br />\n<a href=\"https://awards.upmud9.nu/awards/2015/%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%809%E5%A4%A7%E7%8D%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fawards.upmud9.nu%2Fawards%2F2015%2F%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%259C%25809%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%258D%258E&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a120f627\" target=\"_blank\">https://awards.upmud9.nu/awards/2015/%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%809%E5%A4%A7%E7%8D%8E</a><br />\n<br />\n其中一段話立場新聞是是旦旦，中伏以為英國有個華裔議員中文名叫麥大粒(其實佢根本無中文名)，點知佢地個website自己都都打錯，話Alan Mak澄清自己根本無&quot;英文名&quot;，我發現之後留言串左佢兩句，個admin話自己改左，然後就block左我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/azsf15vo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fazsf15vo&h=1409c2b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時捉人打錯字就咁撚串，自己7左就扮無嘢"},{"pid":"9139ac665f6b1981f6dc396beeff04f384e12969","tid":150992,"uid":24805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:32:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時幾高質 係挑到垃圾記者機<br />\n有時就同垃圾記者一樣垃圾,<br />\n好似仲係親熱血公民</blockquote><br />\n邊個都唔親，無人夠佢國際，全部都係抄報，全部都係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n酸臭到不得了"},{"pid":"78238c1347ec4f62dadc3444cfa781d4e09f40c6","tid":150992,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:43:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/upmud9.nu/photos/a.532424150168315.1073741828.532415746835822/1221553537922036/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fupmud9.nu%2Fphotos%2Fa.532424150168315.1073741828.532415746835822%2F1221553537922036%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=5516701a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/upmud9.nu/photos/a.532424150168315.1073741828.532415746835822/1221553537922036/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n好地地一個受訪路人要比你咁樣人身攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f38003bd881acd19ef09bcb0d82c9928064f0d","tid":150992,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:44:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/upmud9.nu/photos/a.532424150168315.1073741828.532415746835822/1217933744950682/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fupmud9.nu%2Fphotos%2Fa.532424150168315.1073741828.532415746835822%2F1217933744950682%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=06c7eec1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/upmud9.nu/photos/a.532424150168315.1073741828.532415746835822/1217933744950682/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個表達根本冇問題<br />\n留言都有人解釋, 條友柒左又唔認"},{"pid":"bdb4f9f2ef